The file

/content/fonts/UMing.ttc

is licensed under the terms of the the Arphic Public License (see APL).
Currently supported charsets:
ISO8859-1,2,3,4,7,9,10,13,14,15  Big5  HKSCS-2004  GB2312-80  as well as
Bopomofo Extensions for Hakka, Minnan (Unicode 5.0) and their MBE variants.
Partly supported:
CNS 11643  GBK  GB18030  Japanese  Korean
AR PL UMing is a font under development, for the project homepage, visit
http://www.freedesktop.org/wiki/Software/CJKUnifonts .


